
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<title>Travel Page</title>
	<link rel="shortcut icon"  href="~/Images/Airplane ico.ico" />
</head>
<body>
	<div id="ourTitle">
		<h1>Trip Risk Evaluator!</h1>
		<h3>This will calculate all earthquakes and tornados in the US!</h3>
		<a href="~/Home/Earthquakes">Want earthquakes instead?</a> or maybe <a href="~/Home/Tornados">just tornados?</a>
	</div>

	<div class="SearchBox">
		<form action="/Home/UserLocation">
			<h4>Pick a location ("City name/state" preferred!)</h4>
			<input id="TextBox" required @Html.TextBox("Location")<br /><br />
			<label for="Start">First Day</label><input type="date" name="StartDate" data-date-inline-picker="true" /><br />
			<label for="End">Last Day</label><input type="date" name="EndDate" data-date-inline-picker="true" />

			<br /> <br />
			<input type="submit" value="Search now" />
		</form>
	</div>
	<div id="UpperLeftBox">
		<p>Want some states with high tornado volume?</p>
		<p>Type these into the search!</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Texas</li>
			<li>Kansas</li>
			<li>Oklahoma</li>
			<li>Florida</li>
			<li>Nebraska</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
	<div id="leftBox">
		<p>Want to check out some locations with heavy earthquake data?!</p>
		<p>Type these into the search!</p>
		<ul>
			<li>San Francisco, California (Or just "San Fran")</li>
			<li>Anchorage, Alaska</li>
			<li>Hilo, Hawaii (Or you can just type "Hilo"!</li>
			<li>Portland, Oregon (Or just "Portland")</li>
			<li>Seattle, Washington (Or just "Seattle")</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
	<div id="BothPics">
		<img src="~/Images/ShakesAndQuakes.jpg" width="375" height="auto" />
		<img src="~/Images/Tornados.png" width="375" height="auto" />
	</div>
</body>
</html>
